The Final Riot (Live) - Paramore [2008]


The Final Riot! is an official live album by Paramore and was released on November 25, 2008 with a bonus DVD containing the full live concert.

The Concert was filmed on August 12, 2008, at the Congress Theatre in Chicago on the The Final Riot! tour.	

The Final Riot! was certified Gold by the RIAA on March 17, 2009, selling over 500,000 copies.
